{"tid":659510,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"到底珍寶套餐有幾多種食法，邊種先係正宗？","createTime":"2018-05-10T01:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T17:04:17.000Z","uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ac28be72cb6ae54be64a672b9ee2b6916bb8f9ab","tid":659510,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:08:11.000Z","msg":"首先第一個問題係果兩塊包夾咩：<br />\n有聽過夾果醬，就咁夾扒都有，亦有人加舊蛋落去。夾熱香餅都聽過。最離譜聽過有人將舊包當熱香餅咁落糖漿切黎食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就係d調味料點落：<br />\n糖漿主流當然係落落熱香餅到，但都聽過落落舊包到<br />\n落落野飲到都見過<br />\n鹽同胡椒粉通常都係落蛋到，落薯餅都有<br />\n牛油落熱香餅落蛋都有<br />\n果醬我諗係最大爭議，落薯餅落扒落熱香餅都見唔少（未見過落蛋）<br />\n<br />\n其餘仲有d非主流食法，例如兩塊熱香餅夾扒/薯餅。熱香餅點牛奶食，"},{"pid":"e153c480724db8a91afd8823e9a475b7386f735a","tid":659510,"uid":131259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"正宗咪搽包果jam 唔係包jam仲可以用係邊<br />\n不過我通常切一塊包一塊豬柳咁夾住食"},{"pid":"fc7d683a4409c79fc1cecea41cfbe5441b00effb","tid":659510,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5860ec7bbeeed1266ef4d6669142d7d55a52d93","tid":659510,"uid":18913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:15:26.000Z","msg":"除左蛋全部切碎點糖漿"},{"pid":"5b6d5129236bfe74121090c1e7c71fd1b6611a3d","tid":659510,"uid":60341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:16:38.000Z","msg":"不嬲胡椒粉落野飲"},{"pid":"8303399e61a6c16de7bc27692e7daf36abaef696","tid":659510,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:16:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32b106a174d0978b489ebe1e7d0304de09e3cfb2","tid":659510,"uid":159228,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:19:15.000Z","msg":"我表示 我細個係落蛋架！<br />\n細細個覺得 包同扒係一對 熱香餅同牛油糖漿一對<br />\n咁果醬就一定係加落蛋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後食左好多年 直到有一日比人笑on9 <br />\n我先知無人咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cea226a4878e995d849f39bbc0c423d529fb15","tid":659510,"uid":46231,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"我第一時間會dum鳩左個包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蛋就落黑椒<br />\n熱香餅之後有花生醬就花生醬牛油<br />\n依家無就糖漿牛油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f015721bf8c861b37f2734c44016829d0ba4cbf0","tid":659510,"uid":88235,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:22:46.000Z","msg":"首先嗌餐野飲要飲奶昔<br />\n拎左餐之後打開個蓋 <br />\n要先大力索一野 拎起2塊包皮 均匀咁查滿果醬<br />\n合埋佢 浸落杯奶昔到 再打開佢 每邊奶一下<br />\n之後用最大力一野拍落你隔離條友塊臉到<br />\n咁呢個時候條友一定呆撚左 所以打蛇隨棍上<br />\n將剩低果d野拍埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8cbc82141576a0c4ba6b5f26a111bcb7c55857","tid":659510,"uid":89665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"糖漿牛油熱香餅<br />\n包搽果gem<br />\n薯餅落鹽<br />\n蛋 豬柳落黑椒"},{"pid":"238bce2936e5b25ec43a9d780cdaa742c4c6ab91","tid":659510,"uid":81671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"點食關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"70a7a9418e44c92faf08078bcde5f1bb3cb8c7bd","tid":659510,"uid":89665,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec8cbc82141576a0c4ba6b5f26a111bcb7c55857","tid":659510,"uid":89665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"糖漿牛油熱香餅<br />\n包搽果gem<br />\n薯餅落鹽<br />\n蛋 豬柳落黑椒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"Jem <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27d961eb703a0551738f99cecd9298939705aac","tid":659510,"uid":44082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"不嬲拎曬去榨汁先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319ca1463fdcdde2cd40c98f5da7bcb37490ee89","tid":659510,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"我應該係最特別,我會將落剩既鹽同黑椒淋落2塊包到,之後直接食,無醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab084036572cb72a95f81ca4abd39cb22698544","tid":659510,"uid":34767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"扒jam包<br />\n蛋鹽胡椒<br />\n熱香餅牛油糖漿"},{"pid":"e94b26ba900058d98553c6661d506bb59cd83ac3","tid":659510,"uid":26332,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"最正宗係每樣分開食，享受每件食物唔同特質"},{"pid":"1ce560e9df5ee1195680dda876f1269f94bdb8f1","tid":659510,"uid":168385,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"窮到冇錢食珍寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到你地一個二個喺度討論真羨慕"},{"pid":"8e0da2b6110b7ecbad07507aa13802ffde3d3a1c","tid":659510,"uid":120935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:28:43.000Z","msg":"都係屎 點食有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f928615977b9c588d7753bdf5dc492c294f29072","tid":659510,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"will it blend?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ab9eba39cea94f84f4f6fe6814c7902620e05f","tid":659510,"uid":22557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:32:43.000Z","msg":"先食薯餅<br />\n牛油+糖漿配熱香餅<br />\n果jam搽半塊扒<br />\n包搽果jam+半塊扒+半份蛋<br />\n淨係食蛋或加少少胡椒<br />\n最後拎埋對面塊薯餅食"},{"pid":"50d329c5503f441d3b469af1efca2f5cdd291aa3","tid":659510,"uid":87560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"熱香餅加果醬<br />\n包夾扒<br />\n蛋加黑椒"},{"pid":"e2789ac44021d98f10e5cf55bc6821ea9c20e619","tid":659510,"uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:02:59.000Z","msg":"問佢攞茄汁點薯餅都正路"},{"pid":"8017be2603df191fcf79e452512b8171de21cfe0","tid":659510,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"果醬落包<br />\n糖醬牛油落餅<br />\n鹽黑椒落蛋<br />\n扒就咁食"},{"pid":"6f66f41bcddddef0a68633cee7eeb78d5205c909","tid":659510,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"我係除左熱香餅之外全部夾曬入包<br />\n包先搽jam，鹽同黑椒落蛋<br />\n然後就包＞肉＞薯餅＞蛋＞包咁夾住黎咬<br />\n熱香餅就牛油加syrup"},{"pid":"9c84cbc2021fe5420e871cd7dc9e28e7e23d771d","tid":659510,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"豬柳加熱香餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}